The paper deals with a logic for a security infrastructure, which falls under the category of cryptography and security (cs.CR). The paper also discusses the semantics of the logic, which involves logical reasoning and inference, making it relevant to the category of logic in computer science (cs.LO). The paper also mentions the relationship between the logic and logic programs, which falls under the category of programming languages (cs.PL). The paper also discusses the implementation of queries, which involves distributed computing (cs.DC) and software engineering (cs.SE).
